tes candlestick signals, including both the appearance of each but in context on an actual stock chart. It further takes the reader through the rationale of reversal and continuation signals and demonstrates the crucial importance of confirmation (in the form of other candlesticks, traditional technical signals, volume, momentum and moving averages). Michael C. Thomsett is a market expert, author, speaker and coach. His many books include Mathematics of Options, Real Estate Investor’s Pocket Calculator, and A Technical Approach to Trend Analysis. A video of the author titled "Candlesticks for Option Timing" can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IItH6OLh7TI  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aInvestment analysis. 0aStock price forecasting. 0aStocksvCharts, diagrams, etc. 0aStocksxPricesvCharts, diagrams, etc. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Investments & Securities / Stocks.2bisacsh  aCandlestick.  aInvesting.  aOptions.  aReversals.  aStick patterns.  aTrading options.  aTrend patterns.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017z978311062526408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2017z9783110547740oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97815015072980 cprintz978150151580440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150150739740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501507397423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501507397/original  a978-3-11-062526-4  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017b2017  a978-3-11-0